            <title>[LUCENE-2776] indexwriter creates unwanted termvector info</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2776</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed today that when I build a big index in Solr, I get some unwanted termvector info, even though I didn&apos;t request any.&lt;br/&gt;
This does not happen on 3x - not sure when it started happening on trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
